VzEqqSUWNjw.title: Post Malone - AUSTIN (Official Live Performances) | Vevo
VzEqqSUWNjw.description:
Post Malone - ‚ÄòAUSTIN‚Äô Official Live Performances

Post Malone was never simply one thing. His skills are as broad as his artistic vision is vast ‚Äì and it‚Äôs always been that way. Listen to ‚ÄúWhite Iverson‚Äù again. That 2016 nugget was just as much a pop fever dream as it was a cornerstone of Soundcloud rap. Seems like our hero has been in perpetual evolution since day one. Connect the dots between ‚Äòbeerbongs & bentleys‚Äô and ‚ÄòTwelve Carat Toothache‚Äô and you‚Äôll see a lot of territory being covered in a very logical and very compelling way. Now we‚Äôre waiting for ‚ÄòAustin,‚Äô Posty‚Äôs latest and perhaps most revealing work to date (his real name is Austin Richard Post). It arrives July 28, and the singer has told fans that it‚Äôs ‚Äúsome of the most challenging and rewarding music for me, a least ‚Äì trying to really push myself and really do some cool stuff.‚Äù To celebrate the arrival of his fifth full album, we united with Mr. Malone in SoCal last month. The results are stellar, with Post being deeply candid and deeply expressive for the cameras. Geographically and emotionally, he does it all in these three performances - strumming a guitar poolside in ‚ÄúGreen Thumb,‚Äù anguishing on the couch in ‚ÄúOverdrive,‚Äù and balancing on the roof in ‚ÄúSomething Real.‚Äù Here‚Äôs to Post, here‚Äôs to Austin.

hggjZ-FGGkw.title: Post Malone - Overdrive (Official Live Performance) | Vevo
hggjZ-FGGkw.description:
Post Malone - Overdrive | Vevo Official Live Performance

Post Malone was never simply one thing. His skills are as broad as his artistic vision is vast ‚Äì and it‚Äôs always been that way. Listen to ‚ÄúWhite Iverson‚Äù again. That 2016 nugget was just as much a pop fever dream as it was a cornerstone of Soundcloud rap. Seems like our hero has been in perpetual evolution since day one. Connect the dots between ‚Äòbeerbongs & bentleys‚Äô and ‚ÄòTwelve Carat Toothache‚Äô and you‚Äôll see a lot of territory being covered in a very logical and very compelling way. Now we‚Äôre waiting for ‚ÄòAustin,‚Äô Posty‚Äôs latest and perhaps most revealing work to date (his real name is Austin Richard Post). It arrives July 28, and the singer has told fans that it‚Äôs ‚Äúsome of the most challenging and rewarding music for me, a least ‚Äì trying to really push myself and really do some cool stuff.‚Äù To celebrate the arrival of his fifth full album, we united with Mr. Malone in SoCal last month. The results are stellar, with Post being deeply candid and deeply expressive for the cameras. With a fetching pop perspective, he‚Äôs leveling up once again, no doubt. Check this performance of ‚ÄúOverdrive,‚Äù one of the 17 songs from the new album, and stay close as we roll out more performances soon.
